            <li>A: <a href="https://geoloqi.com/users/new">Sign up for a Geoloqi account</a> (or <a href="https://geoloqi.com/session/new">login</a>) and click <a href="/admin">this link</a> to go to the Game Admin page.</li>
            <li><strong>Q: My friends and I can't find a game - what gives?</strong></li>
            <li>A: You probably aren't in the place where you made your game, you haven't walked outside and given the GPS a change to warm up.</li>
            <li><strong>Q: The MapAttack app is still using my location on the phone!</strong></li>
            <li>A: You can either force quit the app or ask your game master to click the "End Game" button on the game creation screen. Game masters can click the "End Game" button in the <a href="/admin">Admin Panel</a> and it will stop the game and show the final score.</li>
          </ul>
